@startuml UC_Sub
skinparam conditionStyle diamond
title Activity: Manage Subscription
|Employer|
start
:Go to Billing / Subscription;
|System|
:Fetch Current Plan Info;
:Display Plan Details;
|Employer|
if (Upgrade/Renew?) then (yes)
  :View Available Plans;
  :Select Plan;
  :Proceed to Payment;
  |System|
  :Redirect to Payment Gateway;
  if (Payment Success?) then (yes)
    :Update Subscription Status;
    :Unlock Features;
    :Show Success Message;
  else (no)
    :Show Payment Error;
  endif
else (no)
endif
|Employer|
if (Cancel?) then (yes)
  :Click Cancel Subscription;
  :Provide Feedback;
  |System|
  :Process Cancellation;
  :Set Expiry Date at Period End;
  :Show Confirmation;
else (no)
endif
stop
@enduml
